name: PYROMANIC S. FORK CANYON
description:
Introduction

This was a continuation exploration of the additional upper forks of Pyromaniac Canyon (completed 3-13-13). We re-joined the main canyon after the new fork, and then continued back down it.

NOTE: see Pyromaniac Canyon in Ropewiki

Approach

Descent

two new rappels in the upper new fork this trip. And then the rest of the dryfall rappels in the original Canyon

Exit

Red tape
